Details :-
    This project is based on users and blogs. There will be 2 roles in the system :- Admin , User. User can create,update ,delete and see their own blogs. Admin can see, update, delete particular user's blog and all blogs.

Install NPM Packages
    - npm install

start command :- npm run start

Migration command :- 
        - npx migrate-mongo up
        - npx migrate-mongo down

Enter following variables in .env
 
    - PORT :- Port on which your app is running.
    - SECRET_KEY :- Secret or key for jwt passport authentication.
    - DB_URL :- Url of your mongodb database.

Roadmap :-

    - Register User 
    - Login User
    - Create blog, find blogs, delete blogs
